==English==

===Transitive verb===
'''[[squeeze]] [[in]]'''

# To find [[time]] or other resources for.
#: ''My appointment book is pretty full, but I can just '''squeeze''' you '''in'''.''

===Intransitive verb===
'''[[squeeze]] [[in]]'''

# To pack tightly together.
#: ''We don't have much room in this car, so everyone will have to '''squeeze in'''.''